steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"9oovc","text":"Add 357 µL 2-(3-chlorophenyl)ethylamine (2.58 mmol, 1.0 eq.) to a solution of 290 mg of Cyclopentaneisocyanate (2.58 mmol, 1.0 eq.) in 10 mL of CH2Cl2.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":4,"length":6},{"style":"sub","offset":146,"length":1},{"style":"sub","offset":149,"length":2}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7r899","text":"Add 276 µL Malonyl chloride (2.84 mmol, 1.1 eq.)  dropwise under vigorous stirring over 5 min. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":4,"length":6},{"style":"bold","offset":50,"length":8},{"style":"bold","offset":83,"length":10}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"d78l7","text":"Stir mixture for 1 h and concentrate in vacuo.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":17,"length":3}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
